{"root":{"data":{"id":"d2kmvjzclns0","created":1720490203166,"text":"无人机管理系统","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2kmvu4hj4o0","created":1720490225244,"text":"1.用户登录","expandState":"expand","priority":1},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2kncx2wodc0","created":1720491563870,"text":"用户身份验证","note":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2knguknqgg0","created":1720491871870,"text":"账号错误","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knh90ikmw0","created":1720491903303,"text":"密码错误","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knhbz22ww0","created":1720491909746,"text":"条件错误","note":"如 二维码刷新失败、token更新失败、界面刷新异常","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knrq9pvbs0","created":1720492724507,"text":"注册密码确认异常","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2knd0jt6rs0","created":1720491571422,"text":"用户登录界面","note":"功能描述：用户输入用户名和密码后，系统通过比对数据库中的信息来验证用户的身份。\n执行条件：用户输入用户名和密码，并点击登录按钮。\n执行结果：如果验证成功，用户将进入系统主界面；如果验证失败，系统将显示错误消息，并允许用户重新输入。","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2knmx6v9200","created":1720492347751,"text":"登录账号","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knn1oky340","created":1720492357529,"text":"登录密码","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knn5z7rj40","created":1720492366879,"text":"登录按钮","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kno4phwcg0","created":1720492442479,"text":"记住密码","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knp2zidso0","created":1720492517095,"text":"跳转注册","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2kndmcz9fk0","created":1720491618899,"text":"用户注册界面","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2knpddo1ts0","created":1720492539719,"text":"注册账号","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knq1po9eg0","created":1720492592688,"text":"注册密码","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knq5zxvs00","created":1720492602016,"text":"注册密码确认","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knqkdhsc80","created":1720492633310,"text":"注册按钮","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2knqootqo80","created":1720492642703,"text":"跳转登录","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2knnva0bmw0","created":1720492421952,"text":"退出登录","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2knsk43n9s0","created":1720492789471,"text":"2.地图导航","priority":2,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2ko9sgwt740","created":1720494139850,"text":"地图展示界面","note":"功能描述：通过地图的形式直观展示电力设备的地理位置、运行状态、巡检路径等信息。\n执行条件：系统实时或定期从电力巡检设备、传感器等数据源接收数据。\n执行结果：用户可以在地图界面上清晰地看到电力设备的分布情况、运行状态以及巡检路径等信息。","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2kor2iah6g0","created":1720495493892,"text":"地图放大","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kolsi8fkw0","created":1720495080300,"text":"地图缩小","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2komw0lgl40","created":1720495166305,"text":"距离测量","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kon7giq8w0","created":1720495191212,"text":"面积测量","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2koqwjjvkg0","created":1720495480908,"text":"角度计算","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kp0njzwns0","created":1720496244985,"text":"2D/3D切换","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2kp0ukm1v40","created":1720496260260,"text":"2D地图","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kp0yr1qvs0","created":1720496269356,"text":"3D地图","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2ksiz34pyg0","created":1720506143972,"text":"无人机导航线路","expandState":"collapse","note":"功能描述：创建并管理航线。\n执行条件：用户访问航线规划页面，执行添加、修改、删除对应航线的操作。\n执行结果：航线创建管理成功，可以用于地图上显示。"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2ksmnq2dpk0","created":1720506432694,"text":"起点"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2ksmrftwsw0","created":1720506440782,"text":"分支点"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2ksmxribcw0","created":1720506454549,"text":"终点"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2ksli7dywg0","created":1720506342316,"text":"作业区域"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2koa5cwo7c0","created":1720494167906,"text":"地图定位","expandState":"collapse","note":"功能描述：地图标注允许用户在地图界面上对特定位置进行标记，以便于记录和跟踪重要信息。\n执行条件：用户通过系统界面选择标注工具，并在地图界面上指定标注位置。\n执行结果：地图界面上增加了用户指定的标注信息，方便用户后续查看和跟踪。"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2kol8aeo680","created":1720495036291,"text":"指南针","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kolbvroiw0","created":1720495044113,"text":"起点","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2komlkhttc0","created":1720495143564,"text":"分支点","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kom83n4a00","created":1720495114246,"text":"终点","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2kolxmapc80","created":1720495091430,"text":"目标点","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2konm05ou80","created":1720495222875,"text":"标点定位","note":"功能描述：显示经纬度，如（经纬度：[ 114.54847,38.042804 ]）。\n执行条件：鼠标先点击“标点定位”按钮（最好为单选按钮），然后鼠标左键点击地图某处位置。\n执行结果：标点定位成功后上方显示经纬度，右上方显示关闭按钮。","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2knsximheo0","created":1720492818647,"text":"3.照片研究","priority":1,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2kr8a805wo0","created":1720502485095,"text":"照片分析界面","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2kruutq6c00","created":1720504253956,"text":"编号","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2krv0p9te80","created":1720504266747,"text":"文件名称","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2krv9g9kfc0","created":1720504285794,"text":"存储地址","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2krvr25jjc0","created":1720504324122,"text":"飞机编号","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2krvwfjgfs0","created":1720504335816,"text":"图片类型","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2kryxk4x340","created":1720504573363,"text":"JPGE","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2krz1bdy480","created":1720504581541,"text":"PNG","expandState":"expand"},"chi